Usage: deleteAIoFiller [-help] -cell <fillerCellName>
                       [-inst <fillerInstanceName>] [-prefix <prefix>] {-aioRowCluster <aioRowClusterName> | -allAIORowCluster }

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-aioRowCluster <aioRowClusterName>     # specifies the area I/O row cluster
                                       # name (string, required)
-allAIORowCluster                      # deletes all area I/O filler cells from
                                       # all area I/O row clusters
                                       # (bool, required)
-cell <fillerCellName>                 # specifies the name of the area I/O
                                       # filler cell to delete (string, required)
-inst <fillerInstanceName>             # specifies the area I/O filler instance
                                       # name to delete (string, optional)
-prefix <prefix>                       # specifies the prefix name of the area
                                       # I/O filler cell instance to be removed
                                       # (string, optional)